HEADWORD: Inexpressibles
<hw>In`ex*press"i*bles</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos>
<def>Breeches; trousers; ; underwear generally, especially women's; --
now usually referred to as <altname>unmentionables</altname>.</def>
